#穗稻忠武觀察室 #深度長文 #人文觀察</description><enclosure url="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/HK_SKD_TKO_Tseung_Kwan_O_PopCorn_mall_Pop_Deli_shop_Pop_Mart_Toy_Store_n_visitors_queue_April_2025_R12S_01.jpg/1280px-HK_SKD_TKO_Tseung_Kwan_O_PopCorn_mall_Pop_Deli_shop_Pop_Mart_Toy_Store_n_visitors_queue_April_2025_R12S_01.jpg" type="image/jpeg" length="0"/><media:content url="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/HK_SKD_TKO_Tseung_Kwan_O_PopCorn_mall_Pop_Deli_shop_Pop_Mart_Toy_Store_n_visitors_queue_April_2025_R12S_01.jpg/1280px-HK_SKD_TKO_Tseung_Kwan_O_PopCorn_mall_Pop_Deli_shop_Pop_Mart_Toy_Store_n_visitors_queue_April_2025_R12S_01.jpg" medium="image"/></item><item><title>透明金字塔裡的貝聿銘</title><link>https://polarbear0827.github.io/My-Way/p/2026-06-22-im-pei-light-stone/</link><guid>https://polarbear0827.github.io/My-Way/p/2026-06-22-im-pei-light-stone/</guid><pubDate>2026-06-22</pubDate><description>在羅浮宮的拿破崙中庭，玻璃金字塔看起來像一個已經被巴黎日常吸收的入口：旅人排隊、孩子貼著水池邊走，宮殿立面透過玻璃和金屬網格被重新框住。但在 1980 年代，它曾被視為一個外來物，一個由法國總統親自推動、由華裔美籍建築師貝聿銘放進法國歷史心臟的尖銳問題。¹

